  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373930/extras/481e3beb1035b5b0a402325e6b243c9b.avif?t=1728423642\" width=600 height=113 /></span><strong>Dino Nest</strong> is a management survival game from the developers of Boxing School.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Far away on an ancient island it all begins with a mysterious dinosaur egg in a cave. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373930/extras/02236066b9a2f702647dc9007d843888.avif?t=1728423642\" width=600 height=113 /></span>Experience the unforgiving life for a reptile in the jungle. Lead your pack and make difficult decisions.  All your actions will have impact on your wellbeing and the members of your pack. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373930/extras/c329bf89069d48a8f6d5b98f7d478ea4.avif?t=1728423642\" width=600 height=113 /></span>As you explore the island you will encounter carnivores and herbivores of all sizes. Expand your hunting territory. Keep your pack alive against all odds. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373930/extras/7c68e6a02036580a04a16d9fff82fc99.avif?t=1728423642\" width=600 height=113 /></span>Maintain your nest and keep it secure from dangers. Breed next generation of packhunters and grow them bigger, faster and stronger. Gain experience from hunting to become more lethal predators.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > All your actions will impact on food, water, health and growth status</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Shape and manage your own pack of dinos</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unique events and decisions with direct impact on gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Jungle wildlife interaction with plenty of carnivores and herbivores</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Maintain your nest and hatch next generation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Detailed talent tree for dinosaur pack genetic DNA mutations</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373930/extras/481e3beb1035b5b0a402325e6b243c9b.avif?t=1728423642\" width=600 height=113 /></span><strong>Dino Nest</strong> is a management survival game from the developers of Boxing School.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Far away on an ancient island it all begins with a mysterious dinosaur egg in a cave. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373930/extras/02236066b9a2f702647dc9007d843888.avif?t=1728423642\" width=600 height=113 /></span>Experience the unforgiving life for a reptile in the jungle. Lead your pack and make difficult decisions.  All your actions will have impact on your wellbeing and the members of your pack. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373930/extras/c329bf89069d48a8f6d5b98f7d478ea4.avif?t=1728423642\" width=600 height=113 /></span>As you explore the island you will encounter carnivores and herbivores of all sizes. Expand your hunting territory. Keep your pack alive against all odds. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373930/extras/7c68e6a02036580a04a16d9fff82fc99.avif?t=1728423642\" width=600 height=113 /></span>Maintain your nest and keep it secure from dangers. Breed next generation of packhunters and grow them bigger, faster and stronger. Gain experience from hunting to become more lethal predators.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > All your actions will impact on food, water, health and growth status</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Shape and manage your own pack of dinos</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unique events and decisions with direct impact on gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Jungle wildlife interaction with plenty of carnivores and herbivores</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Maintain your nest and hatch next generation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Detailed talent tree for dinosaur pack genetic DNA mutations</p></li></ul>",
